---
// 결론 문장을 드라마틱하게 마무리하는 Hero 블록
// "왜 Claude Code는 터미널에 있을까?" 포스트의 마지막 섹션용
---

<figure class="closing-hero">
	<p class="closing-hero__lead">AI agent 를 가장 잘 쓰고 싶다면,</p>
	<p class="closing-hero__main">
		AI agent 를<br />
		<span class="closing-hero__em">컴퓨터에서 가장 가까운 곳</span>에 둬야 합니다.
	</p>
	<p class="closing-hero__tail">
		그게 <span class="closing-hero__terminal">Terminal</span> 이에요.
	</p>
</figure>

<style>
	.closing-hero {
		margin: 3rem 0 2rem;
		padding: 2.75rem 1.5rem;
		text-align: center;
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--claude-soft), white 85%);
		border-radius: 16px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(204, 120, 92, 0.18);
		box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(204, 120, 92, 0.08);
	}
	.closing-hero__lead {
		font-size: 1rem;
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
		font-weight: 400;
		margin: 0 0 1.3rem 0;
		letter-spacing: -0.01em;
	}
	.closing-hero__main {
		font-size: 1.85rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		line-height: 1.3;
		color: rgb(var(--black));
		margin: 0;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
	}
	.closing-hero__em {
		color: var(--claude);
		position: relative;
		display: inline-block;
	}
	.closing-hero__em::after {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		right: 0;
		bottom: -2px;
		height: 4px;
		background: var(--claude);
		opacity: 0.3;
		border-radius: 2px;
	}
	.closing-hero__tail {
		font-size: 1.4rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: rgb(var(--black));
		margin: 1.6rem 0 0 0;
		letter-spacing: -0.01em;
	}
	.closing-hero__terminal {
		color: var(--claude);
		font-weight: 800;
		font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
		letter-spacing: 0;
	}

	@media (max-width: 560px) {
		.closing-hero {
			padding: 2rem 1rem;
			margin: 2rem 0 1.5rem;
		}
		.closing-hero__main {
			font-size: 1.4rem;
		}
		.closing-hero__tail {
			font-size: 1.15rem;
		}
	}
</style>
